### @font-face

**@font-face** loads custom fonts from your server or URL.

---

### Basic Syntax

```css
@font-face {
  font-family: 'MyFont';
  src: url('myfont.woff2') format('woff2');
}
```

---

### Multiple Formats (Fallback)

```css
@font-face {
  font-family: 'MyFont';
  src: 
    url('myfont.woff2') format('woff2'),
    url('myfont.woff') format('woff');
  font-weight: normal;
  font-style: normal;
  font-display: swap;
}
```

---

### Font Face Properties

| Property | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `font-family` | Name to use in CSS (required) |
| `src` | URL(s) to font files (required) |
| `font-weight` | Which weight this file represents |
| `font-style` | Which style this file represents |
| `font-display` | How font loads |
| `unicode-range` | Specify character ranges |
| `font-stretch` | Condensed/expanded variants |

---

### Font Display Options

```css
@font-face {
  font-display: auto;      /* Browser default */
  font-display: block;     /* Hide text briefly, then swap */
  font-display: swap;      /* Show fallback, swap when loaded */
  font-display: fallback;  /* Short swap period */
  font-display: optional;  /* Only use if already cached */
}
```

`font-display: swap` is recommended for most sites - users see text immediately.

---

### Multiple Weights

```css
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Open Sans';
  src: url('OpenSans-Regular.woff2') format('woff2');
  font-weight: 400;
}

@font-face {
  font-family: 'Open Sans';
  src: url('OpenSans-Bold.woff2') format('woff2');
  font-weight: 700;
}

@font-face {
  font-family: 'Open Sans';
  src: url('OpenSans-Italic.woff2') format('woff2');
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 400;
}

/* Usage */
body { font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; }
h1 { font-weight: 700; }
em { font-style: italic; }
```

---

### Unicode Range

```css
@font-face {
  font-family: 'IconFont';
  src: url('icons.woff2') format('woff2');
  unicode-range: U+0025-00FF; /* Basic Latin chars only */
}
```

---

### Variable Fonts

```css
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Inter Variable';
  src: url('Inter-Variable.woff2') format('woff2-variations');
  font-weight: 100 900;
  font-stretch: 75% 125%;
}
```

> **Best Practice:** Provide WOFF2 as primary with WOFF fallback. Always use `font-display: swap`.
